Package com.lelanor.projects.codebreakers.evaluators

Interface Evaluator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Codex, MasterMind
    public interface Evaluator
    This interface is the contract for the automatic evaluators. It contains two methods for Combination and Result analysis, used respectively in attack or defense modes.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      this method analyse a Combination Guess vs a Combination Goal.
      Result analyse​(Result result, Combination goal, CombinationLists lists)
      this method analyse a Result comparing it to a Combination Goal and use the CombinationList to find the result within

        Result analyse​(Combination guess,
               Combination goal)
        this method analyse a Combination Guess vs a Combination Goal. It is used by the CodeMaker player

        goal - the Combination to compare with
        Returns:
        a Result expressed according to the GameType

        Parameters:

        lists - the list of all possible Combination according to the range et the combination size
